      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <div class="project">
        <h3>Project 1: Tic Tac Toe Game</h3>
        <p>Designed and developed a classic Tic Tac Toe game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The project implements core game mechanics and provides an intuitive user interface for an engaging gaming experience.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Interactive Game Board: Implemented a 3x3 grid game board with clickable cells, allowing players to make their moves easily.</li>
          <li>Player Interaction: Enabled players to take turns placing their symbols ('X' and 'O') on the game board, with real-time feedback indicating whose turn it is.</li>
          <li>Winning Conditions: Implemented logic to detect winning conditions, such as achieving three symbols in a row (horizontal, vertical, or diagonal), and declared the winner accordingly.</li>
          <li>Game Reset and Replay: Provided options for players to reset the game board and start a new game after each match, ensuring seamless gameplay.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Technologies Used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript </p>
      </div>
